## **Quick Fix Script**

```bash
#!/bin/bash
cd ~/Vortex_UVM_GP/Vortex/hw/rtl/tcu

# Fix #1: DPI scope issue
sed -i '/`include "util_dpi.vh"/d' VX_tcu_pkg.sv
sed -i '/import VX_gpu_pkg::\*/a\
\
    `ifdef SIMULATION\
        import "DPI-C" function void dpi_trace(input int level, input string format);\
    `endif' VX_tcu_pkg.sv

# Fix #5: Parameter scope
sed -i 's/localparam TCU_R\([ABC]\)/parameter TCU_R\1/g' VX_tcu_pkg.sv

echo "✅ Fixes applied"
```

